<section class="hero-section relative overflow-hidden h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- ── TOP: Text content centered ── -->
    <div class="relative z-10 pt-16 pb-4 flex flex-col items-center text-center px-6 shrink-0" id="hero-content">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-brand-dark dark:text-white max-w-4xl">
            Almacena y Transporta<br/>
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-brand-primary to-brand-light">Sin Límites</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            Conecta con espacios seguros y transportistas confiables en tiempo real.
            La solución inteligente para optimizar tu carga y espacio.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <button data-modal="buscar"
                class="hero-cta-btn px-8 py-4 bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-dark text-white font-bold rounded-xl  transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-105 flex items-center gap-2">
                Buscar Espacio
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </button>
            <button data-modal="publicar"
                class="hero-cta-btn px-8 py-4 bg-brand-light/20 hover:bg-brand-light/30 text-brand-primary dark:text-brand-light border border-brand-light/40 hover:border-brand-light/70 font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center gap-2 group">
                Publicar mi espacio
                <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
            </button>
            <button data-modal="transportista"
                class="hero-cta-btn px-8 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 text-brand-dark dark:text-white border border-gray-200 dark:border-slate-700 font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center gap-2 group">
                Soy Transportista
                <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            <div class="flex -space-x-2">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-200 dark:bg-slate-600 border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-800"></div>
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-slate-500 border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-800"></div>
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-400 dark:bg-slate-400 border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-800"></div>
            </div>
            <p>Uniéndose a +200 empresas y conductores hoy.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── BOTTOM: Phone video full-width ── -->
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full flex justify-center flex-1 min-h-0" id="hero-visual">
        <div class="absolute bottom-[20%] left-[8%] w-52 h-52 bg-brand-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] pointer-events-none hidden lg:block"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-[15%] right-[8%] w-44 h-44 bg-brand-light/20 rounded-full blur-[70px] pointer-events-none hidden lg:block"></div>

        <div class="hero-phone-wrap">
            <video
                id="hero-video-light"
                src="/videos/video_app_clean.webm"
                muted playsinline autoplay loop
                class="hero-phone-canvas"
            ></video>
            <video
                id="hero-video-dark"
                src="/videos/dark_video_app.webm"
                muted playsinline autoplay loop
                class="hero-phone-canvas"
                style="display:none"
            ></video>
            <div class="hero-phone-bottom-fade"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Modals (moved to body via JS) ── -->
